# DPorts Generator

This directory now uses `dportsv3` as the active Python generator toolchain.

## Primary CLI

```sh
python -m dportsv3 --help
python -m dportsv3 compose --help
python -m dportsv3 migrate --help
python -m dportsv3 dsl --help
```

## Notes

- Legacy Python v2 `dports` package/entrypoint has been removed.
- Legacy shell scripts remain in this directory for operational parity checks.
- Packaging exports only `dportsv3` from `scripts/generator/pyproject.toml`.
